Money Stuff =0A The nicest thing you can say about the financial industry i=
s that it lavishly =0Arewards correct understanding of the world. If you kn=
ow a thin =0A=0A=0A <https://bloom.bg/41Ygy1y> =0A =0A<https://sli.bloomber=
g.com/click=3Fs=3D825881&stpe=3Ddefault&li=3D12867022&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615=
cf44233be620525&p=3D03112025>=0A=0A=0A=0AWeather traders=0A=0AThe nicest th=
ing you can say about the financial industry is that it lavishly =0Arewards=
 correct understanding of the world. If you know a thing, and other =0Apeop=
le do not know it, financial markets provide an efficient and fairly =0Agen=
eral way to turn your knowledge into large amounts of money. You don=E2=80=
=99t have =0Ato go out and make some product with your knowledge, building =
a factory and =0Ahiring marketers and getting it into stores. You can push =
